review: I consulted the Doctor on 15 Aug 2021 for my son who had a boil. He examined him very well, addressed our concerns, and prescribed required medication which helped in speedy recovery. Despite having a packed schedule, the Doctor is punctual, handles children and parents in a very gentle manner for best possible medicare. Kudos to you Doctor, your staff and the online Practo Team for the brave and relentless efforts delivered through this extra-ordinary pandemic period of 1.5 years in bringing the best medicare to the comfort of peoples' homes.
